ROS 연동 순서
1. ROS코어 실행
	roscore
2. ROS시리얼 열기(서버 또는 파이썬) // 로스 파이썬은 파이썬 기반의 시리얼 서버이다.
	rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py _port:=/dev/ttyACM0 _baud:=115200
	또는
	rosrun rosserial_server serial_node _port:=/dev/ttyACM0 _baud:=115200

3. ROS 토픽 확인해부기
	rostopic type /topic_name
	rostopic echo /topic_name

4. ROS 커맨드 보내기
	rostopic pub topic_name std_msgs/String "hello there"
	rostopic pub topic_name std_msgs/Type "hello there"

	dmesg | grep tty

	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "stop"
	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "go"
	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "cw"
	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "ccw"
	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "init"
	rostopic pub control_motor std_msgs/String "motion"
각각 토픽 : 인자
control_motor : controlCallback
ir_value : ir_msg
encoder_info : enc_msg

5. RQT 실행
rosrun	rqt
	rqt_graph
rosrun rqt_graph rqt_graph

6. 기타
	roslaunch custom_driver run.launch >> 실행하는거야 잊지말자

  How to launch LIDAR turn-table

1. sudo apt-get install ros-VERSION-velodyne

2. sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-rosserial-arduino

3. sudo apt-get install ros-melodic-rosserial

3. sudo usermod -a -G dialout USERNAME (ex. stryx)

4. reboot

5. catkin_make

6. Turn on your lidar

7. Use static ip and connect to lidar (ex. 192.168.1.10)

8. roslaunch custom_driver run.launch

9. rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py _port:=/dev/ttyUSB0 _baud:=57600 
   (Check your USB port and baudrate)

  Then... Finish!!


+ Opt
  If you want to control your motor, just following below commands.
  1. Stop --> rostopic pub /control_motor std_msgs/String stop
  2. Go   --> rostopic pub /control_motor std_msgs/String go
  3. Slow --> rostopic pub /control_motor std_msgs/String slow
  4. Init --> rostopic pub /control_motor std_msgs/String init  (Only when motor is moving)



